skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: spell my name
des: Your name is music to your ears - literally! Tell me your name and I'll try to sign it with a song. If I haven't spelled your name with a song before, just leave a comment in your review and I'll put it on the list of song to sing. You can check back later to see if your name was added.

The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
